snippet.title: Castlevania Dracula X Chronicles Trailer
snippet.description: The debut trailer of Castlevania Dracula X Chronicles, the sidescrolling 3D remake of Dracula X: Rondo of Blood for PSP. The original TurbografX game and Castlevania: Symphony of the Night will also be on the UMD
